comment: Williams (CHA) and Smith (CLE) make incidental contact on the attempt to secure the rebound.
Thompson (CLE) sets the screen on Williams (CHA) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the ruling on the court that Charlotte touched the ball last is overturned. Charlotte is awarded possession.
[Observable in enhanced video] Batum (CHA) moves his pivot foot.
Batum (CHA) makes incidental contact with Dellavedova (CLE) on the drive.
Jefferson (CHA) makes incidental contact with Thompson (CLE) that does not affect his FOM.
Walker (CHA) cleanly strips the ball from James (CLE) on his drive.
Thompson (CLE) and Jefferson (CHA) engage and then separate on the rebound attempt.
Batum (CHA) illegally uses his hands as Smith (CLE) catches the pass in the frontcourt.
Williams (CHA) commits a take foul on James (CLE).
[Detectable with stop watch] The violation is called before 5 seconds elapses and as Lamb (CHA) releases the ball inbounds.
Zeller (CHA) sets the screen on Dellavedova (CLE) and gives him room to avoid the contact.
